                        <interp inst="t18380917-name-424" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES STEVENS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a watchman of St. Bride's. I heard the alarm of "Stop thief"—pursued and took the prisoner in Shoe-lane—he de<lb></lb>livered the watch up to me at the watch-house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380917-name-425" type="witnessName">
