                  </hi>. I was constable of the night—I searched the pri<lb></lb>soner—I found nothing but a street-door key on him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I picked the watch up by the side of a gentleman walking along the street—I was going to make my way home to get a lodging for the night.</p>
